                  , about the hour of nine, in the night of the <rs id="t18150913-195-cd1090" type="crimeDate">13th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150913-195-off1089 t18150913-195-cd1090"></join>, with intent to steal, and burglariously stealing therein, four curtains, value 4 l. and two carpets, value 1 l. the property of the said 
                     <persName id="t18150913-195-person1733">
                        William 
                        Henry Bodkin
                     <interp inst="t18150913-195-person1733" type="surname" value="Henry Bodkin"></interp>
